name: Tlels
content:
Tlels was a Human male who served as a supply officer in the Imperial Army of the reconstituted Sith Empire during the Galactic War with the Galactic Republic. During the Battle of Ilum, he was stationed in the Imperial base camp.
Supply Officer Tlels first appeared in the 2011 video game Star Wars: The Old Republic by BioWare as an Armor vendor on Ilum for the Empire. He was later removed in a restructuring of the armor and vendor systems.
